Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.56,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.26,0:01:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like it's time for us to settle our scores once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I recognize you as a True Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't agree with your talk about fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I, for one, will never use The Barrier of Orichalcos again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But for someone like you who treasures the bonds you have with your Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}do you really intend to use it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:02:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Immortal! Guardian Deathscythe"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Rafael?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must a Duelist like you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do all I am capable of in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take your soul away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to prove that the fate that Lord Dartz showed me is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is the one that defeated Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The true power of The Barrier of Orichalcos that allows you to fight alongside the darkness in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The darkness of the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you really not forget the bonds you have with those Monsters inside this barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Grarl, attack Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resolute Assault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open, Rope of Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster is sent to the Graveyard due to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can discard my entire hand to activate this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are zero cards in my hand, thus I'll Special Summon Kuribabylon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set one card, finishing my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has only 1000 Life Points left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1000 points is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the power of The Barrier of Orichalcos is much more than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, the title of Duel King that you've tainted... Are you able clear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Kuribabylon's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separate into the Five Kuriboh Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Kuribe's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combine to become Kuribandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I activate a Magic Card, Curtain of Black Magic, from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half my Life Points is used to activate this card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can then Special Summon one Black Magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! It's the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, Yugi's Life is now only 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It won't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Black Magician to attack Guardian Elma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magic!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be used when Guardian Monsters are under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can change the position of one Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there are monsters in front, Monsters at the back cannot be attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How despicable! Hiding in the back like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His deck has the strength to use the power of the Barrier effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next I can activate an Equipment Magic specially from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Sword of Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.23,0:05:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saint Sword of Goddess... Is that Monster coming out soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh, I will once again show you a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Guardian Eatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Eatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When there are no Monsters in my Graveyard, Eatos can be Special Summoned without tribute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This overwhelming pressure... like it holds absolute control over everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning Eatos into that form... are you really alright with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this {\i1}really{\i0} the time for you to be worrying about such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi was defeated by that Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman can absorb the Attack Power of the Monsters in the opponent's Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it turn out like this? If it keeps up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Kuribandit's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing Kuribandit, I can draw five cards from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From those cards, I'll add non-Monster Cards to my hand and send the Monsters into the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By doing that, the Monster's Attack Power will be even higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he can draw a card that can go up against Eatos, it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, can you draw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gambled my chance on this draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gambling for the last hand, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to defeat Eatos with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating Eatos's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul of the Sacred Sword!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Attack Power... is 7000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you did not manage to draw the card you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Guardian Eatos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Gospel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card that I wanted was neither a Magic Card nor a Trap Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Electromagnetic Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is in the Graveyard, the player can end the turn at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was such a card in the Graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So fate wants me to continue this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to see Eatos in that evil form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were wrong after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have used The Barrier of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only someone like you who half heartedly believes in the darkness in your heart would think that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon Big Shield Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I change Black Magician into Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll set one card, ending my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its no use, even if you change your Monsters into Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi has two Monsters on his field, but Rafael has four Monsters in play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, if he Direct Attacks..!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time to decide the outcome of fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Guardian Eatos will attack Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Opera of the Spirits!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Silk Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She missed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Now he has only two Monsters in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he can't Direct Attack, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Black Magician is destroyed...Yugi will have no Monsters on his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, if the destiny you speak of is really what is guiding you, then all you have to do is guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess where my Black Magician is located!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One chance out of three...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one that can overcome Black Magician's Defense Power is Grarl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Elma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liberation of Thunder!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the chance is one out of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Guardian Grarl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resolute Assault!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But {\i1}why{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, looks like fate has not made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can this be? Is fate wavering?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn has not ended yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment Magic, Rod of Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rod of Silence, please guide your master towards you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out! Guardian Kay'est!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow we've gotten out of danger for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, although it looks very unfavorable...Yugi is actually forcing his enemy into a desperate state.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate Magic Card, Angel's Charity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw three cards from my deck and then discard two cards from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This time I must draw that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, I've drawn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate The Eye of Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of Timaeus will combine with Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Legendary Dragon, Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Amulet Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Amulet Dragon's Special Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's Summoned, it can absorb a Magic Card from the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It receives an additional 300 Attack Points per card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were eight Magic Cards that I sent to the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amulet Dragon's Attack Power will now increase to 5300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! He can do this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amulet Dragon, attack Guardian Eatos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Distortion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Barrier is pulsing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your attack just now, Eatos is now sleeping in the Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But her corpse will now rise as a new soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eatos is immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the Monster's spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Eatos' Special Effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Eatos is destroyed by a Monster in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Guardian Deathscythe in Defense Position from the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guardian Deathscythe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Guardian Deathscythe's Special Effect, it can equip the Equipment Magic, Great Sickle of Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the special effect of Great Sickle of Grim Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For every Monster in my Graveyard, it gains 500 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell you you intentionally put Eatos in the Cemetery?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Eatos is in the Cemetery, Deathscythe will become the savior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, when Deathscythe is on the field, I'll not be able to Summon or Special Summon any other Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early for an ending speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change Guardian Deathscythe into Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, the Monsters on my field will all be sacrificed except for Deathscythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! You're sending your Monsters into the Graveyard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because four Monsters were sent to the Graveyard, Deathscythe's Attack will increase by 2000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its Attack is... now higher than Amulet Dragon's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm able to surpass the darkness in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe, attack with all your fury!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Amulet Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Requiem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to dodge a fatal wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, is there no other way anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, Yugi hasn't given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you going to do, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Treasure from Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both players draw until they have six cards in their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Special Summon Watapon onto the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll use this card to Tribute Summon Black Magician Girl in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card, ending my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I'll put an end to your struggling as I take your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate the Magic Card, Obedience!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster with higher Attack Power attacks a Monster with a lower Attack Power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the latter must receive the attack in Attack Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deathscythe will attack Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the last attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it shall be the the conclusion of both of our fates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forbidden Requiem!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Pigeon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:19:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can only be used when Black Magician Girl is on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For one turn, it can turn Black Magician Girl into two Pigeon Tokens in Defense Position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set two cards face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is fate always playing around with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it always helping {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this battle ends, something will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me... and you, I wonder how we'll change.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of seeing that change, I'll give it my all for this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my destiny {\i1}that{\i0} strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're unable to recognize when you harm yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and if you aren't aware of the darkness in your opponent's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's impossible for you to understand the pain and sorrow of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For Haga-{\i0}kun{\i1} and even Mai-{\i0}san{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, even the three Musketeers of Doma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't hear the cries of those suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner, this card can save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael, I can finally hear your anguished cries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cries?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Eatos was sent to the Graveyard, when you were sacrificing your Guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart was crying sadly, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what my partner taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't understand the darkness in your opponent's heart, you will never comprehend the pain and suffering of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will shoulder the darkness in your heart alongside you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What utter nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll use this card to wipe away the cries echoing in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to activate this Magic Card from my hand, Underworld - Heaven Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underworld - Heaven Circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you see the Monsters you sent to your Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing, you impudent busybody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the two of them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Rafael from the darkness in his heart, Yugi has activated Underworld - Heaven Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.31,0:23:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the field engulfed in black aura, what Yugi saw was Rafael's sad memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The despair and sorrow of losing his family resulted in the creation of Guardian Deathscythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.28,0:23:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Yugi destroy Deathscythe and save Rafael's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Destroy the Darkness of the Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
